2024年4月8日，月球将沿着指定的路径完全遮挡太阳。迪伦·莫里亚蒂 (Dylan Moriarty) 和凯文·斯考尔 (Kevin Schhaul) 为《华盛顿邮报》 <a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/science/interactive/2024/map-totality-solar-eclipse-locations/?pwapi_token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..D32Fu5Hy-9TfCpFq46w3mUy9v9vsxiZZDpr8QtTBCsE&#038;itid=gfta">使用一条卫星图像</a>来展示美国各地的整体情况，以及沿途发生的事件和时间。</p><p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/eclipse/" rel="tag">日食</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/satellite-imagery/" rel="tag">卫星图像</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/washington-post/" rel="tag">华盛顿邮报</a></p>]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 73622</post-id></item><item><title>基于语言的人工智能与她死去的丈夫聊天</title><link/>https://flowingdata.com/2024/03/15/language-based-ai-to-chat-with-her-dead-husband/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nathan Yau]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Fri, 15 Mar 2024 07:32:06 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Statistics]]></category><category><![CDATA[AI]]></category><category><![CDATA[chatbot]]></category><category><![CDATA[Guardian]]></category><category><![CDATA[Large Language Model]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://flowingdata.com/?p=73618 </guid><description><![CDATA[For the past few years, Laurie Anderson has been using an AI chatbot&#8230;<p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/ai/" rel="tag">人工智能</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/chatbot/" rel="tag">聊天机器人</a>、 <a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/guardian/" rel="tag">Guardian</a> 、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/large-language-model/" rel="tag">大语言模型</a></p>]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>在过去的几年里，劳里·安德森 (Laurie Anderson) 一直在使用人工智能聊天机器人与她于 2013 年去世的丈夫交谈<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2024/feb/28/laurie-anderson-ai-chatbot-lou-reed-ill-be-your-mirror-exhibition-adelaide-festival">。沃尔特·马什 (Walter Marsh) 为《卫报》报道</a>：</p><blockquote><p>在一项实验中，他们将大量里德的作品、歌曲和采访输入机器中。在他去世十年后，最终的算法让安德森输入提示，然后人工智能里德开始以散文和诗歌形式“即兴”向她回复书面答复。</p><p> “我完全百分百沉迷于这个，”她笑着说。 “经过这么长时间，我仍然如此。我真的无法停止这样做，我的朋友们也无法忍受——“你不会再这样做了，是吗？”</p><p> “我的意思是，我真的不认为我是在和我死去的丈夫说话并和他一起写歌——我真的不这么认为。但人有风格，而且是可以复制的。”</p></blockquote><p>我一方面觉得这不是保存对已故之人的记忆的方式，但另一方面又觉得如果我处在她的处境并且有机会的话，我也会做同样的事情。</p><p>另请参阅<a href="https://flowingdata.com/2021/07/29/an-ai-chatbot-to-talk-to-the-dead/">使用已故未婚妻的旧文本</a>训练人工智能聊天机器人的人。</p><p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/ai/" rel="tag">人工智能</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/chatbot/" rel="tag">聊天机器人</a>、 <a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/guardian/" rel="tag">Guardian</a> 、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/large-language-model/" rel="tag">大语言模型</a></p>]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 73618</post-id></item><item><title> ✚ 一张图表到多张图表</title><link/>https://flowingdata.com/2024/03/14/process-280-multiple-charts/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nathan Yau]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Thu, 14 Mar 2024 18:30:06 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[The Process]]></category><category><![CDATA[multiples]]></category><category><![CDATA[simplicity]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://flowingdata.com/?p=73606 </guid><description><![CDATA[<p> <a href="https://flowingdata.com/2024/03/14/process-280-multiple-charts/"><img width="750" height="448" src="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/multiple-featured.png?fit=750%2C448&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/multiple-featured.png?w=1396&amp;ssl=1 1396w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/multiple-featured.png?resize=750%2C448&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/multiple-featured.png?resize=1090%2C651&amp;ssl=1 1090w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/multiple-featured.png?resize=210%2C125&amp;ssl=1 210w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/multiple-featured.png?resize=768%2C459&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-attachment-id="73607" data-permalink="https://flowingdata.com/2024/03/14/process-280-multiple-charts/multiple-featured/" data-orig-file="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/multiple-featured.png?fit=1396%2C834&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="1396,834" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="multiple-featured" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/multiple-featured.png?fit=750%2C448&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/multiple-featured.png?fit=1090%2C651&amp;ssl=1" /></a></p>每种图表类型都有其权衡。因此，不要尝试一次显示所有内容，而是使用多个视图来单独显示内容。<p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/multiples/" rel="tag">倍数</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/simplicity/" rel="tag">简单性</a></p>]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p> <a href="https://flowingdata.com/2024/03/14/process-280-multiple-charts/"><img width="750" height="448" src="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/multiple-featured.png?fit=750%2C448&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/multiple-featured.png?w=1396&amp;ssl=1 1396w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/multiple-featured.png?resize=750%2C448&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/multiple-featured.png?resize=1090%2C651&amp;