t:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 73590</post-id></item><item><title> OpenAI GPT 简历排名中的种族偏见</title><link/>https://flowingdata.com/2024/03/13/racial-bias-in-openai-gpt-resume-rankings/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nathan Yau]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Wed, 13 Mar 2024 08:19:10 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Statistical Visualization]]></category><category><![CDATA[bias]]></category><category><![CDATA[Bloomberg]]></category><category><![CDATA[OpenAI]]></category><category><![CDATA[race]]></category><category><![CDATA[resume]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://flowingdata.com/?p=73572 </guid><description><![CDATA[<p> <a href="https://flowingdata.com/2024/03/13/racial-bias-in-openai-gpt-resume-rankings/"><img width="750" height="434" src="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?fit=750%2C434&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?w=1738&amp;ssl=1 1738w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?resize=750%2C434&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?resize=1090%2C631&amp;ssl=1 1090w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?resize=210%2C122&amp;ssl=1 210w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?resize=768%2C445&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?resize=1536%2C889&amp;ssl=1 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-attachment-id="73573" data-permalink="https://flowingdata.com/2024/03/13/racial-bias-in-openai-gpt-resume-rankings/bias-in-resume-judgement/" data-orig-file="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?fit=1738%2C1006&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="1738,1006" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="bias in resume judgement" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?fit=750%2C434&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?fit=1090%2C631&amp;ssl=1" /></a></p>人工智能正在寻找进入人力资源工作流程以筛选简历的方法。...<p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/bias/" rel="tag">偏见</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/bloomberg/" rel="tag">彭博社</a>、 <a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/openai/" rel="tag">OpenAI</a> 、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/race/" rel="tag">种族</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/resume/" rel="tag">简历</a></p>]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p> <a href="https://flowingdata.com/2024/03/13/racial-bias-in-openai-gpt-resume-rankings/"><img width="750" height="434" src="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?fit=750%2C434&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?w=1738&amp;ssl=1 1738w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?resize=750%2C434&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?resize=1090%2C631&amp;ssl=1 1090w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?resize=210%2C122&amp;ssl=1 210w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?resize=768%2C445&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?resize=1536%2C889&amp;ssl=1 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-attachment-id="73573" data-permalink="https://flowingdata.com/2024/03/13/racial-bias-in-openai-gpt-resume-rankings/bias-in-resume-judgement/" data-orig-file="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?fit=1738%2C1006&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="1738,1006" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="bias in resume judgement" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?fit=750%2C434&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bias-in-resume-judgement.png?fit=1090%2C631&amp;ssl=1" /></a></p><p>人工智能正在寻找进入人力资源工作流程的方式来筛选简历。从表面上看，这似乎是一个不错的想法，直到你意识到人工智能所基于的模型更倾向于某些人口统计数据。对于 Bloomberg 来说，Leon Yin、Davey Alba 和 Leonardo Nicoletti <a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-openai-gpt-hiring-racial-discrimination/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzb3VyY2UiOiJTdWJzY3JpYmVyR2lmdGVkQXJ0aWNsZSIsImlhdCI6MTcwOTg1NjE0OCwiZXhwIjoxNzEwNDYwOTQ4LCJhcnRpY2xlSWQiOiJTQTA1Q1FUMEFGQjQwMCIsImJjb25uZWN0SWQiOiI2NDU1MEM3NkRFMkU0QkM1OEI0OTI5QjBDQkIzRDlCRCJ9.MdkSGC3HMwwUYtltWq6WxWg3vULNeCTJcjacB-DNi8k">对 OpenAI GPT 进行了实验，结果显示出偏差</a>：</p><blockquote><p>当被要求对这些简历进行 1000 次排名时，GPT 3.5（该模型最广泛使用的版本）比其他人更倾向于某些人群中的名字，以至于无法通过用于评估受保护群体的就业歧视的基准。虽然此测试是典型 HR 工作流程的简化版本，但它将姓名作为 GPT 中可能影响招聘决策的偏见来源进行了隔离。采访和实验表明，使用生成式人工智能进行招聘和雇用会带来大规模自动歧视的严重风险。</p></blockquote><p>是的，听起来不错。</p><p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/bias/" rel="tag">偏见</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/bloomberg/" rel="tag">彭博社</a>、 <a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/openai/" rel="tag">OpenAI</a> 、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/race/" rel="tag">种族</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/resume/" rel="tag">简历</a></p>]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 73572</post-id></item><item><title>大学招生的多样性，不考虑种族</title><link/>https://flowingdata.com/2024/03/12/diversity-in-college-admissions-without-considering-race/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nathan Yau]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Tue, 12 Mar 2024 07:25:00 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Statistical Visualization]]></category><category><![CDATA[admissions]]></category><category><![CDATA[college]]></category><category><![CDATA[SAT]]></category><category><![CDATA[Upshot]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://flowingdata.com/?p=73568 </guid><description><![CDATA[<p> <a href="https://flowingdata.com/2024/03/12/diversity-in-college-admissions-without-considering-race/"><img width="750" height="723" src="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/college-admissions.png?fit=750%2C723&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/college-admissions.png?w=1626&amp;ssl=1 1626w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/college-admissions.png?resize=750%2C723&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/college-admissions.png?resize=1090%2C1051&amp;ssl=1 1090w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/college-admissions.